    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>This slender tube is strapped to one forearm and designed to be concealed beneath the sleeve, where the wielder can fire a featherweight&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/weapons/weapon-descriptions/ammunition/ammunition-thrown-darts\">dart</a>&nbsp;with a twist of the wrist.</em></p>\n<p>The launcher functions by means of a tightly compressed spring, and must be reloaded and re-cocked with a separate ramrod as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Full-Round-Actions\">full-round action</a>.</p>\n<p>After firing, the wearer can attempt a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/sleight-of-hand\">Sleight of Hand</a>&nbsp;check opposed by opponentsâ€™&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/perception\">Perception</a>&nbsp;checks to keep the wrist launcher concealed. If you are proficient with hand crossbows, you are also proficient with wrist launchers.</p>",
